Constructor that takes parameters. Used when creating an in-memory object to correspond to an entry in the database

Parameters:
id - ID number
DataMeans_id - ID of corresponding dataMeans
title - Title of the data
url - Raw link to the source
data - Short description of the source
linkUrl - Link to a "normal" (human-friendly) version of the source
linkedData - HTML dump of the source
timestamp - When this source was created
indexed - Indicates whether this source has yet been indexed by Lucene
